Following are guiding principles for creating or learning projects in AI.

Choice of Problems ‚Äì Preference for meaningful or frontier problems over generic use cases.
Demonstrated Obsession ‚Äì Evidence of deep personal drive through self-driven projects, not just checkboxes.
Unique, Quirky Passions ‚Äì Tangible individuality and curiosity that bring novelty to their work.

While practicing also I need to practice or learn by keeping those points in the mind
today I wanted to start creating a project called travel planner . The aim of this project is 
"I want a 5-day trip. Plan flights, hotels, and sightseeing." 

Finally I will ask you to showcase our project as per our guiding principles.
next 3 days I wanted to master Agentic architecture by learning different protocols also


